  "texts": [
    "Table 4: Patent Classification (Lee & Hsiang, 2020; Hain et al., 2020)",
    "As shown in Figure 7, the best result for the F1 score and accuracy had been achieved when we chose 8 nearest neighbors.",
    "In this case, Precision and Recall were 74% and 60%, respectively.",
    "Also we tested the model for class level, results for F1 score was 82.44%.",
    "It is noted that, in this approach, we can increase the Precision score by increasing the number of K nearest neighbors."
  ]
